https://git-scm.com/docs/git-credential-store

# This will create the ~/.git-credentials file
$ git config credential.helper store

# First interaction will setup the user and pass
$ git push http://example.com/repo.git
Username: <type your username> (Use SSO)
Password: <type your password> (Use Github generated Token)

[several days later]
$ git push http://example.com/repo.git
[your credentials are used automatically]
